{"tid":2212170,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃店] 元朗小店台籍老闆突然離世 餐廳去向未明 本週繼續營業","createTime":"2020-09-21T14:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T13:57:41.000Z","uid":143270,"like":82,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"2f0716896c1a9f47ee8a4bc6769891aba39c1f8b","tid":2212170,"uid":143270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:51:17.000Z","msg":"以自製台灣香腸聞名的元朗古月聚，今早網上突然傳出消息，老闆鄭國濱先生上星期五因心臟病而突然離世，記者致電往餐廳查詢，接聽電話的林先生證實消息，老闆家人已從台灣來港處理身後事。消息傳出後，一眾熟客大表震驚，不少人都在網上訴說老闆生前點滴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自高雄的老闆，2007年因和港人太太結婚而搬來香港，發現香港缺乏台灣香腸，所以沿用父親傳授的手藝，在香港新鮮製作台灣香腸發售，大受歡迎，2016年9月在元朗開設餐廳，既賣大腸包小腸，也賣滷豬腳、碗粿等地道台灣小吃。由於老闆一向親手處理小店菜式，家人暫時決定今星期會繼續經營餐廳，屆時再決定未來動向。<br />\n<br />\n採訪、攝影：《飲食男女》<br />\n<br />\n古月聚<br />\n<br />\n地址：元朗馬田路 20-30B號安寧大廈 2號地舖<br />\n<br />\n電話：3705 1396<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/ETW/20200921/4W3VJEJ24JFLHAMBQT5B76Y374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20200921%2F4W3VJEJ24JFLHAMBQT5B76Y374%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=9281f6b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20200921%2F4W3VJEJ24JFLHAMBQT5B76Y374%2F&h=10b2d99e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/ETW/20200921/4W3VJEJ24JFLHAMBQT5B76Y374/</a><br />\n<br />\n老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rip"},{"pid":"06c4501b7f6dd092a00b43c61d72daffa5f89bc1","tid":2212170,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"點解2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c0c96450ae7e53ad3efd98ec699362c92f2c33","tid":2212170,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img sr